{"tid":1610210,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"針對現時最大弊病 解決心態問題","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:15.000Z","uid":11634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d87f9f95a28035b79c65321d7f405fd59fc2a81","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"講真 一見到有狗就走其實已經輸咗9成<br />\n係講緊見到10隻狗都唔夠<br />\n但自己手足過百人都走難咁走<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都未突破到 即使係前線都會驚 會淆<br />\n大部分手足都係年輕人 大學生 甚至中學生<br />\n冇經過任何訓練 只係憑一腔熱血 一顆追求自由嘅心 就出嚟抗爭 甚至上埋前線<br />\n更何況今日真槍實彈都開埋<br />\n話唔驚係假嘅<br />\n<br />\n我地既然知道咗問題所在 係咪應該針對佢嚟改進呢<br />\n我知道BU有 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">練武course</span><br />\n其實可以參考下佢地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舉行啲course比抗爭義士有一個訓練</span></span><br />\n可以教下基本意識 概念 攻防技術等等<br />\n雖然實際效果未必會好大<br />\n但係起碼幫到大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突破心理關口</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認為自己係一個 <span style=\"color: green;\">受過訓嘅人</span></span><br />\n和理非都要一齊參加 務求可以危急時變勇武<br />\n相信今日之後 大家面對嘅武力只係不斷上升<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯狗隻係唔允許進入校園範圍<br />\n就算入咗大家都只係上緊lecture<br />\n大學/學院範圍都多原因可以入<br />\n但詳細需要再安排"},{"pid":"e4faf81e76bb7b71844c871d21996f862259fef0","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"cd16d39190db3437ef244c9c207bddc9d7f968f4","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"2dc0118a9f771182f942d6d534b969bf82f853ce","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"cf4ca8cdc527a221083f263d4fc15ea04539cbc2","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"8fe3a07f8f5fd9d57e11be3bdfc10f1bfc373d6e","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10<br />\n係咪應該開學術定校園台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5435a39e2b93a1a3e95b770969eeda24487cf228","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"ee6c8fcb03a45f4930ee1147b7e5e57627a4f9cf","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10"},{"pid":"8569d46369c757dbf268f460279f684903a971e5","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10"},{"pid":"5a31b24bcb2af48f39328f78eda016ab2f7e76c8","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10"},{"pid":"72286b4254f44bcada72b50802618061a8c31871","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c003e496dbbd207b0e43f1785c7aa87aecf1d7f8","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"推到有人出嚟搞！"},{"pid":"a68fdf446f7eea2660883ba4222c1bd30bfeadf7","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"有冇搞手可以睇一睇"},{"pid":"f740b3149b8025ca3df25b069b9c6ee672c39445","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"或者BU會唔會考慮搞大佢"},{"pid":"5c01572fd5fd19973b7be7a560cc7d8bfbd0c9db","tid":1610210,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}